### Slice and Splice

```js
// SPLICE Returns the removed item(s) if assigned to a variable
// Mutates Original Array

var cities = ["Chicago", "Delhi", "Islamabad", "London", "Berlin"];
cities = cities.splice(0, 2);


// SLICE Returns the selected element(s) in a copy array, 

var slities = ["Chicago", "Delhi", "Islamabad", "London", "Berlin"];
slities = slities.slice(0,2);



console.log(cities);
console.log(slities);
````
